{
  "texts": [
    "Stained cells were analyzed by flow cytometry on an Accuri C6 plus flow cytometer (BD) and analyzed using the manufacturer's software.",
    "pRPA32s33 and γH2AX staining.",
    "Trypsinized cells were resuspended in 1 mL PTEMF buffer and incubated for 20 min.",
    "5 mL DPBS was added to quench the PTEMF buffer.",
    "Fixed cells were resuspended in 1 mL blocking buffer, then incubated for 1 h before adding primary antibodies (pRPA32s33, 1:200; γH2AX 1:400) in 100 µL blocking buffer."
  ]
}